<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/baaf1b9045e441c7a497fba801429869.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/8dc9bf6797054cf58960d4609096ed1f.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/0f74ff2df6ea4761a2b495c664669ec1.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/fa95e72d396142c5a0bd0e96928c34b4.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/afd63b55d4f64aa1836166c5e90e4a57.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>同学们尽情徜徉在这花的海洋，洋溢着青春的喜悦。日落时分，适逢一辆拖拉机经过，大家朝司机挥手，司机大叔停了下来，载了同学们一程，还帮同学们搭了小客车，直到大家都上了车，那位大叔才挥手和同学们道别.......</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/75f4689992974e618d6ae8a92031b7c5.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/e552394bd3814217987aa9003315d472.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>大家从金川出发去甲居蔵寨，依然是盘山而行。海拔越来越高，道路颠簸，少数同学稍微有点不适，同学们互相照顾着。透过窗户，寨子依着起伏的山势迤逦连绵，一幢幢藏式楼房洒落在绿丛中，或在高山悬崖，或在河坝绿洲间。又见充满灵气的山谷，烟云缭绕，溪谷清澈，雪峰皑皑......</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/3c82d284d3cf4962afddbf5599118e84.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/38700477b98545e6be209995bef7739a.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/c27230e1aa034a5b939ecf3257c8e9c3.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>学们住在甲居藏寨自由写生，静心描绘着田园牧歌式的中国最美乡村画卷。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/b69527e1da4547679239847f9994f96f.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/24ca9a391ac544fc9542f086af2aa008.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/083225269bc748bd925e411d5e114b43.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/8588a1baf0d14016948a05023afa1f7a.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/04b5cd7962274fed8b11a35745df53d3.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>大家还去了塔公、新都桥。当翻越海拔4298米的折多山垭口时，放眼望去山峦叠嶂，白雪皑皑，石垒玛尼堆与舞动的五彩经幡……山川之大美让同学们心底沸腾！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/b858a96d135d47229df614ee5777d844.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/d058e06f0af249d18e42a5a8a19afa82.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/d24285cae94e44569a0de784d7482733.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/0579daee787a4036bef960b6e6c4f7be.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>快乐的时光总是过得很快，不觉便到了最后一站—大渡河峡谷。大渡河峡谷两岸山峻，峰奇，石怪，绝壁深谷连为一体，神秘的景观令大家惊叹。观峡谷，画峡谷，运笔之际，眼前笔法纷呈。那裸露的岩石，线条横竖错杂，可大小斧噼而为之，又可马牙皴就，亦可用枯笔焦墨，纵笔挥写，以笔法之千变万化摹造化之千姿百态。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/5ced0ea7cbfa437689f5f506d5bd782c.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/cb7f727e7e204881bee526db59d8118d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/d9c029551a72471298ffae928c54ecbb.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/bbd23d375bb3428bad4808beae9af312.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/96e034487d5b4187b90a69c94c027639.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/94c15d169f9a4f9ca8dd360e63fb5567.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/d6e74f9a7f7e43b68baff7c9690f32c1.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/c79cc01f97374a818be1c66770beaae5.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/f306a8218bed4157b93d8e424e4dd5b1.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/5df09e7fd1b04a41b279acf6ad367b00.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/44479ce704a24f459bb742ccf728df11.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200821/0e9124a3d30442f290bc0c24df6ceb60.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>4月5日一早，同学们拎着行李依依不舍地返校。返校后，大家更加觉得那段日子意犹未尽。10天的时间说长不长，说短不短，对所有人来说都很珍贵，不仅收集到素材，还让同学们感受到集体在外的生活中，老师的关怀和同学间的友爱。相信不管是专业还是友情同学们都会越走越远，越走越深。</p>